AUTO-OWNERS INSURANCE COMPANY, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
Julie SHAFFER and Todd J. Bunnell, Trustee of the Bunnell Living Trust, Defendants-Appellees. SC: 158879
COA: 343841 Supreme Court of Michigan. February 14, 2019

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motion of plaintiff-appellant to extend the time for filing its replies is GRANTED. The replies submitted on February 12, 2019, are accepted as timely filed.
